美国武装部队的不同分支由不同的标志、徽章和[[军旗|军旗]]所代表。在同一分支内，不同旗帜会在不同时候使用，亦会悬挂在不同船只、基地和军事学院。

基本情况下，悬挂军旗时的先后顺序为：美国国旗、美国陆军军旗、美国海军陆战队军旗、美国海军军旗、美国空军军旗和美国海岸防卫队军旗<ref name="Precedencedod">{{Cite web|url=http://permanent.access.gpo.gov/websites/dodandmilitaryejournals/www.dtic.mil/whs/directives/corres/html2/d10058x.htm|title=DoD Directive 1005.8|accessdate=2009-04-07|date=October 31, 1977|last=Duncan Jr.|first=Charles W.|authorlink=Charles Duncan, Jr.|work=[[United_States_Deputy_Secretary_of_Defense|Deputy Secretary of Defense]]|publisher=[[United_States_Department_of_Defense|Department of Defense]]}}</ref><ref name="precedencevet">{{Cite web|url=http://www.veteransinfo.net/Main%20page/flags_seals_order_of.htm|title=United States Military Order of Precedence|accessdate=2009-04-07|last=Terrel|first=Captain|publisher=veteransinfo.net|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081011063740/http://www.veteransinfo.net/Main%20page/flags_seals_order_of.htm|archivedate=2008-10-11}}</ref> 然而，在美国海岸防卫队作为美国海军一部分运作时，例如在战时，美国海岸防卫队军旗会排在美国空军军旗前。<ref name="precedenceflags">{{Cite web|url=http://flagspot.net/flags/us%5Emil.html|title=Order When Displayed|accessdate=2009-04-07|date=2008-04-26|last=Wyatt|first=Rick|publisher=[[Flags_of_the_World|Flags of the World]]}}</ref><ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20060503075909/http://www.tioh.hqda.pentagon.mil/FAQ/FAQ.htm Frequently Asked Questions Page] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060503075909/http://www.tioh.hqda.pentagon.mil/FAQ/FAQ.htm |date=2006-05-03 }}</ref>

